# Drop .desktop files here to hide or override app launcher entries.
#
# To hide an app from walker/wofi, create a file matching the app's
# .desktop name (find originals in /usr/share/applications/) with:
#
#   [Desktop Entry]
#   NoDisplay=true
#
# Example: to hide btop.desktop, create btop.desktop here with NoDisplay=true.
# https://specifications.freedesktop.org/desktop-entry-spec/latest/
